results.name: Decimal expansion of 3*sqrt(2)*Pi^3/128.
comment: Equals the value of the Dirichlet L-series of the non-principal character modulo 8 (A188510) at s=3. - _Jianing Song_, Nov 16 2019
reference: L. B. W. Jolley, Summation of series, Dover Publications Inc. (New York), 1961, p. 64 (formula 340).
link: G. C. Greubel, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
formula: Equals Sum_{i >= 1} A188510(i)/i^3 = Sum_{i >= 1} Kronecker(-8,i)/i^3. - _Jianing Song_, Nov 16 2019
results.author: _Bruno Berselli_, Dec 10 2014
